        "items": [
          {
            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### A Common Pattern\n\nCompare these sentences:\n\n- Ти **прочитав** книгу? - Did you read the book?\n- Ні, я **не читав** її. - No, I didn't read it.\n\nNotice: The question uses perfective, but the negative answer uses imperfective!\n\nThis is a fundamental pattern in Ukrainian: **negation prefers imperfective**."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
